title: Five Below
description:
Shop Five Below trends *literally* everywhere now! YES! New to the fam? We’re extreme $1-$5 value, plus some incredible finds that go beyond $5. All waaay below the rest…so ‘let go & have fun’ with one of the coolest brands on the planet!
Reasons to Download
Easy Peasy to Use!
We’re obsessed with extreme value and finding you an unbelievable steal! Experience effortless browsing, fast searching for those specific things that you just gotta have, and quickly find one of over 950 stores nearest you!
Shop Without Worry
You told us, and we listened! Welcome to an even BETTER Five Below mobile experience! Discover an easier checkout, faster shipping, and smoother shopping from beginning to end! Checkout securely using your credit/debit card, or now with PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Pay.
What We’re Bringing
We’re constantly adding new stuff! Check back often for our latest drops in toys & games, Bluetooth earbuds, fitness & wellness gear, makeup, graphic tees, art supplies, candy, books, room décor & more!
$5 Shipping
Receive $5 shipping on any order (big or small!) Shop 1000s of items right now!
All the Latest Trends & Fave Brands!
Bluetooth, LEGO, Disney, Marvel, Squishmallows, Hershey, JoJo Siwa, Crayola, EOS, Freeman, Sour Patch Kids, Trolli, Haribo & lots more!
Love us? Tell us!
We heart our customers, and welcome feedback to make this app even better! Leave a rating and review! And be sure to hang out with us on Instagram, TikTok, Facebook & Twitter. @fivebelow
Whether you’ve grown up with us, or you’re new here---download the Five Below app to start shopping the newest, trendiest, coolest stuff! (A good decision all around!)
